<p><strong>Popular in Malaysia because:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Preserves working capital (70-90% of equipment cost)</li>
<li>Immediate use without full cash payment</li>
<li>Fixed monthly payments (easier budgeting)</li>
<li>Builds business assets (appears on balance sheet)</li>
